                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-15-off75 t18220522-15-cd76"></join>, one handkerchief, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220522-15-victim166" type="victimName">
                           William 
